{
  "meta": {
    "repo_path": "tests/mb-vectors.json",
    "version": "mb-vectors 1.1 — thermo core + six core modules, vectors MB-001..MB-040",
    "target": "api/_lib/mb-engine.js (mb-engine 0.6.x, parts 1+2 — thermo core + module solvers)",
    "units": "T [K], P [bar(a)], molar h [kJ/mol], Cp [J/mol·K], stream H [kJ/h]",
    "notes": "Expected values are EXTERNAL references (NIST WebBook, IAPWS-IF97 steam tables, SVN App. C, CRC/Perry class values) — never engine output — so these vectors detect coefficient transcription errors, not just regressions. Groups: A gas Cp/H (Shomate+SVN), B water/IF97, C Watson latent heat, D phase determination edge cases, E formation-basis reaction consistency, F solveT_forH round-trips. Group G (MB-026..MB-040): module solvers via runModule — mixer, splitter, flash (Rachford-Rice), heat-exchanger, rotating (pump/compressor/turbine), conversion reactor; expected values are hand calculations from steam tables, published Antoine constants, ideal-gas relations, and Felder & Rousseau-class worked figures — never engine output."
